Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,DECEMBER 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] What was that? Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid L is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but how?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Kira? Did Kira kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Roger. You've got to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Roger] Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But he promised me he'd find Kira\Nand execute him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you're telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that he's been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Roger] Mello…\N-[clatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] If you can't win the game…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't solve the puzzle…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're just a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which of us did L pick?\NMe or Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He hadn't chosen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that he's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't the two of you work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] It'll never work, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I don't get along with Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always competed against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[wind howling outside]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Near should be the one to succeed L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not like me.\NHe never gets emotional,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he just uses his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like it's a game or a puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving this institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Don't waste your breath.\NI'm almost fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] It's time I started living\Nmy own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,MARCH 5, 2012
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] A police officer who happened\Nto be nearby during Higuchi's arrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,overheard him talking about the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you write a person's name in it\Nwith their face in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that person will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you're saying\Nthis notebook of death actually is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point the Japanese police\Nshould have it in their possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A YOUNG MAN NAMED NEAR PRESENTS\NEVIDENCE ON THE KIRA CASE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,WHICH HE'S GATHERED BY HIMSELF\NOVER THE LAST THREE YEARS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,HE MEETS WITH THE PRESIDENT,\NACCOMPANIED BY THE DIRECTOR OF THE FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, the current L is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was created by the Japanese police
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to avoid confusion and panic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst the various\Ninternational police agencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The real L is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Director Mason…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Near is... Well, in a sense\Nyou could call him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the true successor to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,CREATES THEIR OWN INVESTIGATION TEAM\NINDEPENDENT OF L TO GO AFTER KIRA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SPK\N(SPECIAL PROVISION FOR KIRA)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,IS COMPOSED OF HAND-PICKED\NFBI AND CIA AGENTS ALONG WITH NEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ABDUCTION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] But still, it's impossible for us\Nto censor everything on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And we haven't had\Nany new leads in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But posting names and faces online?\NI'm sorry, but if you ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the people doing that\Nwho deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira gets a lot of his information\Nfrom the internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's not gonna kill those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggles] Matsu, you silly,\Nyou've got it all backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Still, I can imagine\Nhow some people must feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To them, the world's become a good place\Nfor people who don't commit any crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, it's a good place\Nfor innocent people who lead good lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk cackles]\NLook who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon everyone in the world\Nwill think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all still talking\Nabout that Kira business?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give it a rest\Nfor one afternoon, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Light, you too.\N-[Sayu] I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how's it going? [giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just having tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Light, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Seems like it's been forever, you two.\N-[Matsuda gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, we missed you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you must be... Mr. Matsuda, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always\Ntaking such good care of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammering] Geez, Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I saw you, you were this big...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa laughs] Matsu, your face\Nis going bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is? I mean... no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let Sayu marry a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never want that for my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really? Oh, man.\N-[Misa giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got the chance to propose,\Nor even tell her I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too cruel to me, Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-"Mom"?\N-"Dad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I think you'd be\Na good catch, Mr. Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so, Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. In fact, I was thinking\Nif you were a little younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have considered\Ngoing out with you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess my little sister\Nis all grown up, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-She's already way more mature than Matsu.\N-[Yagami scoffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course,\NLight hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just as wonderful and handsome\Nas when I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already got\Na career and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it official.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stop living together secretly\Nand just get married already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming scene
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,from the most unfortunate family\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? What is it, Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[Light and Matsuda] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, Light, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] A kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Involving who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They got Director Takimura of the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure who's behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we don't have enough\Non our plate already with the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,DEPUTY DIRECTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the phone call at 6:12.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was about 45 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we were able to confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that the call originated\Nfrom the director's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the kidnappers make any demands\Nin terms of ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted to trade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the director for the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Who's behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And for what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not. If the existence\Nof the notebook has been leaked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there could be any number of people\Nwho'd want it for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, did you say anything to the director\Nabout the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We all agreed to keep the information\Nbetween the six of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he didn't know, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I never told the director,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so he couldn't tell the kidnappers\Nanything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone knows about the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they know\Nthat the Japanese police have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, they've come to claim it\Nfor themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Notify every bureau\Nin the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-But only about the kidnapping itself.\N-[Aizawa] Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone beeping]\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Has there been a call from the suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] No. There's a visitor here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,who wants to meet\Nwith the Director Takimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] My name is John McEnroe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an agent with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is just an alias.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As my assignment involves Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a necessary precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to unforeseen circumstances,\Nthe director is unavailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's acceptable,\Nyou can speak with me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, I'll get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese police have proven themselves\Nto be unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in order to solve the Kira case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we want you to hand over\Nthe notebook to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the FBI was behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-[McEnroe] What are you talking about?\N-[Yagami] Don't act like you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a serious criminal offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[McEnroe] What would the FBI gain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by capturing the director\Nof the Japanese NPA?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By the sound of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems that the director\Nof the Japanese police force
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-has been kidnapped by someone.\N-[Rester groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Specifically, someone\Nwho wants the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Commander Rester.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass on this message to our agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Suggest to the Japanese police\Nthat we'd like to assist them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in rescuing the director\Nand apprehending the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the notebook\Nonce we have the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] Attention! This is headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have new orders for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[footsteps echoing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[metal door creaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[director groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he decided to say anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He told us the Japanese police
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,had begun to wimp out on Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like right now\Nthe only ones officially working for L
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,are Soichiro Yagami, Kanzo Mogi,\Nand Touta Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There was also Ukita,\Nbut he was killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And as a top cop\Nsomehow you didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that this notebook even existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or that you had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]\NJapanese cops must be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the investigators\Non the task force,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Director Yagami\Nwould be the highest ranking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takimura] Ye-- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My theory is that\Nthere are two notebooks out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them is in Kira's possession,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the other is with the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna take both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we do what Mello says,\Nthere will be no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a year and a half\Nsince he joined us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and in that entire time\Nhe's never been wrong about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but that's what's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was able to bring us\Nthe head of a mafia boss
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that even Kira himself couldn't kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,why the hell would he even\Nneed the notebook to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] It's not just the notebook\NI'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eliminate my competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[cracks]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I will beat Near by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[man chuckles] Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-[laughter]\N-[Pedro] B-- Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NCan't you see that I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But Eddie and I were\Ntalking for a minute and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Takimura hung himself\Nwith his tie somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do\Nwith a dead hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-No, this'll be just fine.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira is responsible for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we know he can't touch us\Nsince he doesn't know our names or faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he went after Takimura instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Kira is someone\Nwho knows about the kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That should make things\Nrather... interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Glen] So, what are we gonna do, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what are we gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna kidnap\NSoichiro Yagami's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] We still haven't been able\Nto find any leads
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,on either Director Takimura\Nor the kidnappers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are getting pretty weird
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they should've contacted us\Nby now with further demands
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out the real name\Nof the FBI agent John McEnroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,According to his personnel file\Nhe is actually called Larry Conners.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, that's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also a genuine agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His background and credentials check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the director of the FBI has offered\Nto help us rescue Director Takimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure\Nwe'll be able to trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the director should\Nalready by dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't the kidnappers\Nsaid anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they gonna give up on the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just because they lost\Ntheir bargaining chip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think our opponents\Nwould be such pushovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, Dad, and the rest of you too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we're gonna have to be\Nextremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The director might not have known\Nabout the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but he does know\Nwho was originally working with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible the kidnappers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-might come after us.\N-[Misa] Hey, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[men] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a good girl\Nand go to bed by myself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Guess I'll hang out around here.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It just occurred to me.\NWe're not the only ones in danger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Our families are at risk.\N-[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] A call\Nfrom the director's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Quick, Aizawa!\N-Got it! Tracing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Look. About trading the director\Nin exchange for the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the deal's been cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Takimura is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-[all] Huh?\N-[Yagami] You bastards! What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] It's only canceled, though,\Nregarding the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The new deal is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the notebook for Sayu Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See, as you're the deputy director\Nof the Japanese police,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be stupid to ask you\Nnot to call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But you had better handle this\Non your own, without backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see the police making\Nany big movements
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in the next little while,\NI'll kill your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, just as easily\Nas we killed the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a photo of Takimura's corpse\Nto prove I mean business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll contact you tomorrow.\N-[call ends]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! They got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They used the director's death\Nas an opportunity to get to Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things\Nare getting interesting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-can't believe they'd go this far.\N-Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-[Sachiko] Yes, yes, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, you usually never call\Nfrom your work phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you mention it,\Nshe is late getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone buzzing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,BIG BROTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was Kira\Nwho killed the director,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,not the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[men] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably did it because he doesn't want\Nthe notebook to fall into the wrong hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira claims to be justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't want the notebook\Nused by someone evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If he killed the director,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's reasonable to assume
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he has ways of obtaining information\Nfrom within the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we should be the ones\Nwho investigate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We leave the police out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will find out about it\Nand probably kill the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And we can't take that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we've just received a report
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that the director\Nof the Japanese Police Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] I see. By whom?\N-"By whom?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... The kidnappers, of course. Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-if it turned out to be Kira.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] That's a very good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The police won't be\Ntrading their notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,if the hostage is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so it protects Kira's interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it is in fact Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can narrow down\Nour list of suspects significantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Commander Rester…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been able\Nto determine his whereabouts yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're able to confirm that he\Nleft the institution four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But nothing beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Very well. That clinches it.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Mello, you never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You always overlook\Nthe most important things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because you let your emotions\Nget the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you're not even\Ninvolved in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you leave your photo\Nbehind at the orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Your daughter has finally arrived.\NIt's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] You already have a pretty\Ngood idea of where we are, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] We'll make the exchange here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to LA by yourself in two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course,\Nbring the notebook with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] I won't make the trade\Nunless I'm sure my daughter is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] How about this?\NI'll send you another photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That should satisfy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-[call ends]\N-[murmurs nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[both murmur nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpers] Oh! Sayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chief, we've narrowed the call down\Nto Fifth Street in LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I just checked out the show\Nthat was playing in the background
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's being broadcast right now\Non a local LA station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've shown us that\Nso we'd know the photo is recent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we know she's still alive.\NThat's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the notebook to Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my decision, both as deputy director\Nof the Japanese Police Force
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and as Sayu Yagami's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take full responsibility\Nfor the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my final word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad. Before we do anything,\Nwe have to come up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, Chief. We can't rush in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to be in LA in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're telling me\Nis that Kira killed Takimura,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,not the kidnappers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm simply putting it forward\Nas a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it does turn out to be true,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then it means Kira must be\Ngetting his information
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone beeps]\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light in distorted voice] This is L.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already heard what investigator\NJohn McEnroe, or rather Larry Conners,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,had to say to Deputy Director Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in regards to the notebook\Nin the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help us\Nwith the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,into NPA director Takimura's murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass me the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-[rattling over phone]\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to meet you at last,\NL number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Number two?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you mean by that?\N-[men] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really no point\Nin trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We are a new organization\Nknown as the SPK,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or "Special Provision for Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was established\Nto find and capture Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,without the help of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[in distorted voice]\NFurthermore, seven of our top members
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,already know of L's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] They do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they hear that?\NWho the hell told them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the center of the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can address me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as N.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] N?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[chains rattling]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...this strange feeling, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]